Class CircleTile

    java.lang.Object
    org.cove.jade.surfaces.AbstractTile
    org.cove.jade.surfaces.CircleTile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Surface
public class CircleTile
extends AbstractTile
implements Surface

Class implementing a circular tile. This is a fixed object in the world with a circular surface that primitives/particles can collide with.
